  "text": "A PPI network was generated to infer the interactions among proteins. The PPI network was constructed using the Search Tool for the Retrieval of Interacting Genes and proteins (STRING) database (https://string-db.org/) [CITATION_1] . To explore the regulatory mechanisms, interactions with the highest confidence of a combined score >0.900 were imported into Cytoscape to construct the PPI network.",
